{"type": "article", "id": 6005, "title": "Edgy 瓷砖", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-09T07:34:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233930A4Q3xqbt2auNkgmG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t波兰设计师 Patrycja Domanska 与 Tanja Lightfoot 的设计师们日前联手为瓷砖制造商 Kaza Concrete 带来了一组瓷砖作品 Edgy。它由两种不同的瓷砖组成，加入了 3D 立体造型的元素，既可以用于公共空间，也适合私人的居家环境，室内室外皆可使用。不管是选择覆盖整个墙面还是部分装饰，都有令人惊喜的点缀效果。3D 立体造型瓷砖的不对称表面，呈现出的视觉效果也很别致。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233928dN1srbwWkYjD23B4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233928BnmzWNDSYi6XERko.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233929EuDqI1bpK87f9vJN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233929DcBVgPZU4uLIny7R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233930ASuhkEvq1eJQl5G4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}